[src:computational-fluid-dynamics/finite-volume-method] Equation (**7**) is *exact* for the volume averages; i.e., no approximations have been made during its derivation.
[src:computational-fluid-dynamics/finite-volume-method] This method can also be applied to a 2D situation by considering the north and south faces along with the east and west faces around a node.
